        <div>
            <h2>The Product</h2>
            <p> <a href="url">belasartes.pt</a> is the institutional website of FBAUL. It aims to be the place where students, staff and potential candidates can access services, know about events related to the school and all information related to FBAUL.</p>
        </div>
</section>

<section class="case_studies_content_2columns">
    <h2>Briefing Breakdown</h2>
    <div>
        <p>We were given the task of developing concrete solutions to improve the user experience of the <strong>Alumni segment on the FBAULs website.</strong></p>
        <p>Unlike other segments, there was <strong>dedicated space on their platform for Alumni...</strong></p>
    </div>
</section>

<section class="case_studies_content_2columns">
    <div>
        <h2>But... Why should FBAUL care?</h2>
        <p>A strong relationship between an institution and their alumni can be hugely beneficial to both of them...</p>
    </div>
    <ul>
        <li>
        <details>
            <summary><h3>Global Awareness ↗</h3></summary>
            <p>Alumni provide positive awareness which boosts application rates and reduces the need for recruitment efforts.</p>
          </details>
        </li>
        <li>
            <details>
                <summary><h3>Increased Success ↗</h3></summary>
                <p>Supporting alumni improves their chances of having a successful career, which will boost FBAULs reputation.</p>
             </details>
        </li>
        <li>
            <details>
                <summary><h3>Mentorship ↗</h3></summary>
                <p>Alumni can be great role models for current students and are usual open to offer mentorship and career support.</p>
            </details>
        </li>
        <li>
        <details>
            <summary><h3>Loyalty ↗</h3></summary>
            <p>They are loyal to their institution and have the potential to become students again, or even staff.</p>
          </details>
        </li>
    </ul>
</section>

