<section class="case_studies_content_2columns">
    <div>
        <h2>Our discovery approach</h2>
        <p>This is how we we got the main insights that informed the development of our solution</p>
    </div>
    <ul>
        <li>
        <details>
            <summary><h3>User Interviews ↗</h3></summary>
            <p>We interviewed 7 FBAUL alumni from different majors and education levels. We registered and organized their testimonies and later turned them into problem statements.</p>
          </details>
        </li>
        <li>
            <details>
                <summary><h3>User Survey ↗</h3></summary>
                <p>We conducted a survey with over 45 alumni of multiple background, schools, majors and education levels. We later cross analyzed the results and turned them into hypothesis.</p>
             </details>
        </li>
        <li>
            <details>
                <summary><h3>Benchmarking ↗</h3></summary>
                <p>We looked at 6 different Portuguese public and private schools to understand their approach to maintain a relationship with their alumni.</p>
            </details>
        </li>
    </ul>
</section>

