<section class="case_studies_content_1column">
    <h2>What were the insights that informed our solution?</h2>
    <ol class="casestudies">
        <li>
          <img src="https://freight.cargo.site/t/original/i/e78673ebf00c8426dbee7550e62e3a14e265109277543cae80b008185a345d11/ProblemStatements_1.jpg"></img>
          <figcaption>
            <h3>Lack of information for applicants</h3>
            <div class="description">
              <p>Candidates need to know the real benefits and experiences of being a student at FBAUL because it will help them asses if FBAUL is the right place to achieve their goals.</p>
              <p>Most candidates are aware that FBAUL is a “prestigious” place to study through alumni they have talked to.</p>
            </div>
          </figcaption>
        </li>
        <li>
            <img src="https://freight.cargo.site/t/original/i/6669eaeda4512c127896f8a7aea96eaacafddada19f774bb2859df7d87296919/ProblemStatements_2.jpg"></img>
            <figcaption>
              <h3>Lack of information about events</h3>
              <div class="description">
                <p>Alumni living in Lisbon need to know information about FBAUL events.</p>
                <p>Alumni living outside of Lisbon/Portugal need to be able to be involved in events just like other alumni, because they would be interested in participating in these events.</p>
              </div>
            </figcaption>
          </li>
          <li>
            <img src="https://freight.cargo.site/t/original/i/ee304a1830c54ec21c8ed5651321191108dffc9a54604d3f6be719aa4f4a534c/ProblemStatements_3.jpg"></img>
            <figcaption>
              <h3>Difficult access to important documents</h3>
              <div class="description">
                <p>All graduates need easy access to their diploma to officially prove they studied at FBAUL and get access to the job market, research opportunities, other courses etc as soon as they graduate.</p>
              </div>
            </figcaption>
          </li>
          <li>
            <img src="https://freight.cargo.site/t/original/i/b804a81ac703ebb4fd6cbf1d98531f4b03c0807539541f7c7949a65cc6c0fb68/ProblemStatements_4.jpg"></img>
            <figcaption>
              <h3>Lack of promotion of alumni work</h3>
              <div class="description">
                <p>Alumni developing projects need to see their work being recognized and represented by FBAUL because their work would have a bigger chance of being seen by the community.</p>
                <p>Alumni developing projects need a way to openly share their work with FBAUL because recognition from FBAUL, colleagues and teachers could bring new opportunities.</p>
              </div>
            </figcaption>
          </li>
          <li>
            <img src="https://freight.cargo.site/t/original/i/f1409a4c91b8f70c0c3ef3d3b06b08650ffc6e9bf8323e2634fa3298cead6c19/ProblemStatements_5.jpg"></img>
            <figcaption>
              <h3>Inexistent mentorship programs</h3>
              <div class="description">
                <p>Alumni would like to inspire other people, by sharing good professional experience with new students because it would give them a sense of belonging and recognition from FBAUL. </p>
              </div>
            </figcaption>
          </li>
          <li>
            <img src="https://freight.cargo.site/t/original/i/d3fd670f6237ea8bb7ae6346b99830c29614b54b15aaecc0b35a18a47fa38d3f/ProblemStatements_6.jpg"></img>
            <figcaption>
              <h3>Poor connection to the market</h3>
              <div class="description">
                <p>Recent Graduates need to have access to trustworthy employers because they are more vulnerable to precarious and exploitative companies, that are rampant in these fields.</p>
                <p>Recent Graduates need guidance and resources on how to build a portfolio that is up to industry standards.</p>
              </div>
            </figcaption>
          </li>
          <li>
            <img src="https://freight.cargo.site/t/original/i/a42e51ff49e0c2199d94fedb679057ba31585441b1c5912e83c3792f2094feea/ProblemStatements_7.jpg"></img>
            <figcaption>
              <h3>Weak connection to former classmates</h3>
              <div class="description">
                <p>Alumni who are interested in other fields of study need to be able to connect with students in other fields to build new connections.</p>
                <p>Alumni need a way to stay in contact with former classmates that doesn’t die down over time because contact with former classmates increasing their chances of a successful career.</p>
              </div>
            </figcaption>
          </li>
</section>

